# üü¢ SUPABASE CONFIGURATION
# Get these from: https://supabase.com/dashboard ‚Üí Settings ‚Üí API
# ‚ö†Ô∏è  Only use anon key for client-side, never service_role!
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL=https://your-project-id.supabase.co
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=your-anon-key-here

# üî¥ SUPABASE SECRETS (Server-side only)
# ‚ö†Ô∏è  NEVER use NEXT_PUBLIC_ prefix for secrets!
# These are only accessible on the server
